                  "content": "Scale: 4 / 8 / 12 / 16 / 24 / 32 / 40 / 48\nCards: 16–20 padding\nSections: 24–32 gap\nEditorial blocks: 40–48\nRadius: 12 inputs, 16 cards, 20 hero, 28 nav",
